# gr-signal-restart - verify ze signal recognizes restart command
#
# Tests that the "restart" command appears in ze signal usage.
# The actual SSH exec is tested by SSH integration tests.
#
# VALIDATES: AC-9 -- ze signal restart is a recognized command.
# PREVENTS: "restart" missing from signal dispatch.

cmd=foreground:seq=1:exec=ze signal
expect=exit:code=1
expect=stderr:contains=restart
